	%script{:src => "js/modernizr.js"}

	%body

	-# ==========================================================================
	-# Content
	-# ==========================================================================

	%header
		%h1 Fate RPG Stuntmaker
		%p
			Randomly create stunts for the
			%a{:href => "http://fate-srd.com"} Fate RPG

	%article.main-content
		.wrapper
			.notice.hide-js
				This tool requires Javascript to function. Either turn on Javascript or open it in a browser that has it activated.
			.add-cards
			%a.button.hide-no-js{:href => "#"} Show me more stunts!
			.notice.hide-no-js
				%strong These are meant to provide a starting-point.
				Be careful about thoughtlessly grabbing them and dropping them into your game without at least a little table-vetting and checking for potential unintended side-effects!


